page.title: 09A TYPICAL DAY-JONATHAN OWEN
page.content: To start my day would be to wake up at ten past seven and turn on the television and watch Popeye.After that I would get out of my bed, get dressed and wake mum and dad up.I live in a post office and my dad wakes up at half past seven to let the post men in.I have one brother,he is called Mark,my name is Jonathan.After getting mum and dad up I would get my breakfast which varies from cereal toast to porridge or an apple.After that I would get my football gear ready and my crisps,then stick my bag just outside our door and then play with our visitors baby for half an hour.When our taxi comes it beeps its horn.Our taxi is Jason and Kevin's mum because they come to our school too.It is a white Cortina and is fast.When we get to school it is about five to nine, our school opens at nine o'clock
